.SH NAME
SDL_GetScancodeFromKey \- Get the scancode corresponding to the given key code according to the current keyboard layout\[char46]
.SH HEADER FILE
Defined in SDL3/SDL_keyboard\[char46]h

.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #include \(dqSDL3/SDL.h\(dq
.PP
.BI "SDL_Scancode SDL_GetScancodeFromKey(SDL_Keycode key, SDL_Keymod *modstate);
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Note that there may be multiple scancode+modifier states that can generate
this keycode, this will just return the first one found\[char46]

